    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/244658de9cfbe7f0f5366b715fa1637d.avif?t=1690359905\" width=684 height=302 /></span><br><br>在魔幻的异世界，你可以探索神秘的地下城堡，幽闭可怖的深邃地牢，环境多变的无边洞窟，一个光怪陆离的深渊地底世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/7707b97f68bd18b144bfb6300bf85146.avif?t=1690359905\" width=616 height=292 /></span><br><br>在充满未知的旅途中，你可以欣赏辉煌壮观的远古城堡，也可以游走在光怪陆离的自然风光中，当然你更有可能遭遇到各种各样强大的怪物，击败它们，克服种种困难，才是这段旅途真正的意义所在。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/e358bbdecbf6fcd2542c6ab459a2a110.avif?t=1690359905\" width=620 height=90 /></span><br><br>经典的横板动作游戏，角色操作感十分丝滑，且拥有丰富的操作空间：二段跳，滑铲，爬墙，蹬墙跳等等。<br><br>开放广袤的魔法城堡世界，错综复杂的道路通往不同的地方，你可以自由选择前进的道路，不用害怕走错路，你可以随时掉头，但是一定要小心别迷了路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/79a4da3b3065f6f1bde487724079f7b9.avif?t=1690359905\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>游戏中有几十种不同的武器，不同的武器能带来截然不同的战斗方式，寻找出最适合自己的强大武器吧。<br><br>搜寻强大的卷轴！探寻远古的能量！这些古老的宝藏是你旅途中不可或缺的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/574af728aeeea0ae5f83a12854b1a236.poster.avif?t=1690359905\" width=514 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/574af728aeeea0ae5f83a12854b1a236.webm?t=1690359905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/574af728aeeea0ae5f83a12854b1a236.mp4?t=1690359905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>3D的游戏场景带来华丽的视觉盛宴为游戏世界带来独特的层次感，同时也描绘出魔法文明的炫丽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225510/extras/f95af65d7da1d660b2f45dc353a00b69.avif?t=1690359905\" width=684 height=302 /></span>",
